      • parseCacheAnnotations

        public Collection<CacheOperation> parseCacheAnnotations(Class<?> type)
        从接口复制的说明: CacheAnnotationParser
        Parses the cache definition for the given class, based on a known annotation type.

        This essentially parses a known cache annotation into Spring's metadata attribute class. Returns null if the class is not cacheable.

        指定者:
        parseCacheAnnotations 在接口中 CacheAnnotationParser
        参数:
        type - the annotated class
        返回:
        CacheOperation the configured caching operation, or null if none was found
        另请参阅:
        AnnotationCacheOperationSource.findCacheOperations(Class)
